  Q. Did you did he tell stung by a bee out there today?  
 SERGIO GARCÃA: I did, on the 14th, it was funny, early morning, just the fifth hole, I hit my drive on 14 on the par 5 and hit it a little bit left. I was walking off the tee and I felt like I had something on the back of my hat and I kind of thought maybe it was a leaf or maybe a little bug or something and I went to scrape it off, and it stung me on the finger.   
